RT @chasmaxson: Here's a formula in Google Sheets that returns the number of followers for a Twitter user: 

=VALUE(REGEXEXTRACT(REGEXREPLA…
retweet_text:
Here's a formula in Google Sheets that returns the number of followers for a Twitter user: 

=VALUE(REGEXEXTRACT(REGEXREPLACE(IMPORTXML("https://t.co/HxHR9e6ijV","/"),"\n"," "),"(?:Following)(.+)(?:Followers)"))

Change to use others or simply replace with a formula (e.g. A2)
